Port and any future credentials should come from env vars, validated at boot:

```js
const PORT = Number(process.env.PORT) || 3000;
if (!Number.isInteger(PORT) || PORT < 1 || PORT > 65_535) {
  throw new Error('Invalid PORT');
}
